Detailed Description

Holds CPSW EEE (Energy Efficient Ethernet) Per-Port STATUS.

Field Documentation

Uint32 CSL_CPSW_EEE_PORT_STATUS::rxFifoEmpty

CPSW port receive FIFO (switch ingress) is empty - contains no packets

Uint32 CSL_CPSW_EEE_PORT_STATUS::rxLpi

CPSW port receive LPI state - asserted when the port receive is in the LPI state

Uint32 CSL_CPSW_EEE_PORT_STATUS::txFifoEmpty

CPSW port transmit FIFO (switch egress) is empty - contains no packets

Uint32 CSL_CPSW_EEE_PORT_STATUS::txFifoHold

CPSW port transmit FIFO hold - asserted in the LPI state and during the LPI2WAKE count time.

Uint32 CSL_CPSW_EEE_PORT_STATUS::txLpi

CPSW port transmit LPI state - asserted when the port transmit is in the LPI state

Uint32 CSL_CPSW_EEE_PORT_STATUS::txWake

CPSW port transmit wakeup - asserted when the port transmit is in the transmit LPI2WAKE count time.

Uint32 CSL_CPSW_EEE_PORT_STATUS::wait_idle2lpi

CPSW port wait idle to LPI - asserted when port is counting the IDLE2LPI time
